            <span class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>

        <span content="2012-04-08" class="main-meta">2012-04-08 10:59:20</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://movie.douban.com/review/5379572/">侠之大者——徐克的《黄飞鸿系列》</a></h2>

                <div id="review_5379572_short" class="review-short" data-rid="5379572">
